Ontario Teachers’ May Sell Control of Maple Leaf Sports, Globe Reports

-- B y   D a v i d   S c a n l a n
-- 
2011-03-13T01:30:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-13/ontario-teachers-may-sell-control-of-maple-leaf-sports-globe-reports.html
The Ontario Teachers’ Pension Plan
said it will consider selling its 66 percent stake in Maple Leaf
Sports and Entertainment, owners of the Toronto Maple Leafs
hockey team and the Toronto Raptors basketball club, the Globe
and Mail reported.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Scanlan at 
 dscanlan@bloomberg.net  